Winds May Be Shifting For Big Turbine Makers --- Renewable-Energy Use Is Poi=
sed to Spread --- But the Most Lucrative Markets Have Little Breathing Room
By Keith Johnson
Staff Reporter

08/13/2001
The Wall Street Journal Europe
9
