dations about how Texas could help fight global warming.=20
Saitas said TNRCC officials may conclude that new state actions specifically=
 targeting greenhouse emissions are not warranted, because pollution-cutting=
 efforts already under way are also eliminating a large volume of these gase=
s.=20
